parameters:
\SE[12]You never learn, do you... You're doing it on purpose,
aren't you...

\SE[4]Well, it's fine. \SE[1]It's refreshing to catch glimpses of
your skin color. It cheers me up.
\SE[5]There's... a witch who can cure Luna... ahead, right?
The 'Snow Forest' has been added to the teleportation crystal!
